{"tid":2224160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五金店存逾百公升天拿水等危險品　消防考慮檢控","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T10:27:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"38660b496fe0705e69f97b266c057efb35194409","tid":2224160,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"消防處突擊巡查屯門一間五金店，發現約104公升懷疑第五類危險品，包括天拿水、白電油和松節油，五金店一名男子涉嫌違反《危險品條例》，處方考慮向他作出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n消防處已將涉案的懷疑第五類危險品檢走，並會繼續打擊有關違法行為，主動對化工原料店及五金店進行突擊巡查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552488-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552488-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kymAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=bcffb3f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552488-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3deba2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552488-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9d87161336867f35a72238d400d18145428a747d","tid":2224160,"uid":57671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"置樂間黃店？"},{"pid":"63813ca3ea55ac9c215a3c24521d2a58950c543c","tid":2224160,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21c927029644ecf51f545ca6c6411d03370386d9","tid":2224160,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"過量?定係跟本唔比賣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa74a34486e7f497bfcf33aed2fc5d3d1bc66886","tid":2224160,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"尋日荃灣都有間5金奶野"},{"pid":"43101bf430027cb7a314fe408a655cd6944186c9","tid":2224160,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":